          "evidence_text_excerpt": "About the offer\nTo get the offer:\nOpen your first Scotia High Interest Savings Account (HISA). You must not currently have a Momentum PLUS Savings Account or a Scotia HISA or have held either account within the last 2 years\nYour Total Relationship Balance 1 must be over $10,000 CAD each day to earn interest on your Scotia HISA for that day. This is calculated by adding up the daily closing balances in your Scotia HISA and all your other eligible accounts\nThen, for the first 3 months you have your account, you\u2019ll earn both the:\nPromotional rate of 2.80% 2\nRegular interest rate of up to 2.20% 3\nInterest will be applied to your Scotia HISA only when:\nThe Total Relationship Balance is greater than $10,000 CAD\nYour Scotia HISA is open and in good standing",
